    "For the sake of clarity, we introduce here the details of the experimental settings used to obtain the results discussed in this Section and in Sect. 4.3.",
    "Evaluation Protocol.",
    "We follow the experimental setup for UDA proposed in Damen et al. (2022), where the finegrained nature of the dataset annotations combined with the large domain and temporal shifts between the source and target domains make the adaptation task very challenging.",
